{%- comment -%}
  LE FIGUE — cart packaging chooser (2026-07-21).
  Per-ORDER choice: Full packaging (+$2, default) vs Reduced (free).
  Charged via hidden product "Full Packaging" (handle full-packaging,
  variant 52110086013226, type "Packaging" — excluded from the `all`
  smart collection by TYPE != Packaging rule, seo.hidden=1).
  The $2 line is added/removed by assets/lefigue-custom.js AT CHECKOUT
  CLICK (never while browsing), so cart re-render fights are avoided;
  leftover packaging lines (customer backed out of checkout) are
  scrubbed on page load. Choice persists in localStorage lf:packaging.
  Rendered in sections/quick-cart.liquid + sections/main-cart.liquid.
  Styles: custom.css Edit #26.

  Accepts: context — 'drawer' | 'page' (unique radio group names).
{%- endcomment -%}

{%- liquid
  assign lfp_real_items = 0
  for item in cart.items
    unless item.product.type == 'Packaging'
      assign lfp_real_items = lfp_real_items | plus: 1
    endunless
  endfor
-%}

{%- if lfp_real_items > 0 -%}
  <div class="lf-pack" data-lf-pack>
    <div class="lfp-head">Packaging</div>
    <label class="lfp-opt">
      <input type="radio" name="lf-packaging-{{ context | default: 'cart' }}" value="full" checked>
      <span class="lfp-txt">
        <span class="lfp-t">Full packaging</span>
        <span class="lfp-d">Signature box &amp; ribbon</span>
      </span>
      <span class="lfp-pr">+$2.00</span>
    </label>
    <label class="lfp-opt">
      <input type="radio" name="lf-packaging-{{ context | default: 'cart' }}" value="reduced">
      <span class="lfp-txt">
        <span class="lfp-t">Reduced packaging</span>
        <span class="lfp-d">Delivered in a LE FIGUE pouch</span>
      </span>
      <span class="lfp-pr">Free</span>
    </label>
  </div>
{%- endif -%}
